{"tid":966135,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平稱不承諾對台灣放棄使用武力","createTime":"2019-01-02T14:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T17:03:33.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"01ff24f6652102914c94af897eda09de81121b46","tid":966135,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/7DE4EEE4-B289-4CA7-91B9-A2322E4D21D1_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F7DE4EEE4-B289-4CA7-91B9-A2322E4D21D1_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=ea28fa5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國家主席習近平表示不承諾對台灣放棄使用武力，並為統一台灣&ldquo;保留採取一切必要措施的選項&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n習近平星期三在北京紀念中國的&ldquo;告台灣同胞書&rdquo;發表40週年的紀念會上表示，&ldquo;祖國必須統一，也必然統一&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n領導中華民國的國民黨1949年退到台灣。從那以來，台灣一直自治。在中國大陸建立了新政權的共產黨數十年以來始終堅持台灣是中國的一個省，終將與大陸統一。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的民進黨年贏得上一次的大選，2016年5月開始在台灣執政。蔡英文政府拒絕承認&ldquo;一個中國、各自表述&rdquo;的所謂&ldquo;九二共識&rdquo;，馬英九擔任總統期間的兩岸交流停擺。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在發出武力威脅時也表示願意為和平統一創造空間。他在講話中說：&ldquo;中國人不打中國人&hellip;中國人要幫中國人。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n台灣總統蔡英文剛剛在2019年新年講話中批評中國沒有及時向台灣同胞提供非洲豬瘟疫情，說如果在疫情防治上都不能合作，哪來&ldquo;兩岸一家親&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n根據台灣陸委會2018年10月底委託台灣政治大學進行的民意調查，主張兩岸廣義維持現狀的人佔絕大多數，達83.4%，其中主張以後再決定的有31.1%、主張永遠維持現狀的有22.3%。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在講話中重申了北京的立場，表示&quot;台灣問題是中國的內政，不容任何外來干涉&quot;。"},{"pid":"90c9c4142f3dc13bc9d588d1241de43ad312094f","tid":966135,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"好奇問下<br />\n其實有幾多國家會經常公開講呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4740bf17f7030c667ed780504de812ed00ac0c91","tid":966135,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"快D打<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1142192c5c7ec8233c653ab5c689e40fbea682","tid":966135,"uid":10208,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"不承諾對台灣放棄使用武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩中文黎，雙重否定句？"},{"pid":"0952d79f51873cd81a5488c1f2d4a8899805e72e","tid":966135,"uid":84297,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b1142192c5c7ec8233c653ab5c689e40fbea682","tid":966135,"uid":10208,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"不承諾對台灣放棄使用武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩中文黎，雙重否定句？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"中文差返去讀書啦"},{"pid":"231ad65d2a5d92ad3ee3bcca3246a79082936bc1","tid":966135,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0952d79f51873cd81a5488c1f2d4a8899805e72e","tid":966135,"uid":84297,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b1142192c5c7ec8233c653ab5c689e40fbea682","tid":966135,"uid":10208,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"不承諾對台灣放棄使用武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩中文黎，雙重否定句？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"中文差返去讀書啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"特登講成咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6975ef88159c5241080624f1717b249872a586b6","tid":966135,"uid":10208,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0952d79f51873cd81a5488c1f2d4a8899805e72e","tid":966135,"uid":84297,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b1142192c5c7ec8233c653ab5c689e40fbea682","tid":966135,"uid":10208,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"不承諾對台灣放棄使用武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩中文黎，雙重否定句？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"中文差返去讀書啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"明佢意思還明佢意思<br />\n但你覺得好通順咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152bdd682146fdcb8d19bd975bcea442524b434e","tid":966135,"uid":84297,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"q